Preheat oven to 350 degrees F. Place chickpeas, 1 cup of the cheese, cream cheese, sour cream and ground red pepper in blender or food processor container; cover. Blend until smooth. Stir in green onions. Spread into 9-inch pie plate. Bake 20 min. or until light golden brown. Top with remaining 1/2 cup cheese and tomato. Serve with crackers.